/// Based on
/// http://ramachandrang.com/2016/04/23/express-angular2-application-using-typescript-server-setup.html
/// and
/// http://ramachandrang.com/2016/05/18/express-angular2-application-using-typescript-Angular2-application.html
/// and
/// http://ramachandrang.com/2016/05/19/express-angular2-application-using-typescript-code-sharing-workflow.html

/// before install run:
-> Install node gyp https://github.com/nodejs/node-gyp
npm install -g git+https://github.com/angular/angular-cli.git
npm install -g typescript typings gulp
/// in root folder run:
npm install && cd client && ng build && cd .. && cd server && typings install